Sculptra stimulates your skins natural collagen production and works subtly, gradually over time for a youthful appearance. 

Sculptra corrects shallow to deep facial wrinkles and folds that appear with aging and restores volume resulting in firming and lifting sagging skin and improved facial contour. 

Sculptra benefits: improved skin laxity, lasts up to 2 years, natural and long term results, smooths out skin texture, and is great for sunken areas that appear by jowls
